@stothemc: [Kaffeesatz Yanone](http://web.archive.org/web/20131016124419/http:/www.identifont.com/show?JQ2) by Jan Gerner.

@kapp2377: Next time start a new thread for your request. BTW, looks like [Marker Felt Wide/Thin](http://web.archive.org/web/20131016124419/http:/www.identifont.com/show?3IP) by Apple.
Excellent! Thank you both so much!
